Dataset 
The model is trained using the GRID Corpus dataset, which contains audio and video recordings of 34 speakers uttering structured six-word sentences. The dataset is commonly used for research in visual speech recognition and lip-reading systems.

Official Dataset: https://spandh.dcs.shef.ac.uk/gridcorpus/

Note: The dataset is not included in this repository due to its size and licensing restrictions. Users must download it separately from the official source.
